                max_total_amount,
                expiry,
                nonce,
                status,
                executed_payments,
                total_paid,
                next_payment_due,
                failure_count,
                created_at,
                updated_at,
                chain,
                avail_block_number,
                avail_extrinsic_index
            ) VALUES (
                $1,
                $2,
                $3,
